creator: Leadoo Marketing Technologies Oy
descriptionHtml:
Take your Leadoo Livechat discussions with you wherever you go with the Leadoo Messenger app. With the Leadoo Messenger mobile application you can access all the same messaging functionalities as in the web application, but also enjoy the freedom of not being tied to a desktop device.

You need a Leadoo Conversion Platform account and an active Livechat module to use this app. You can get your account from here: https://leadoo.com/get-leadoo/
descriptionShort: A mobile messaging app for your Leadoo Conversion Platform.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Leadoo Messaging App is finally out for all the Leadoo Conversion Platform owners. This is our first release and includes all the basic functionality needed to manage your Leadoo Livechat on your mobile device. More updates and fixes are coming soon after the release!

Added support for attachments. Users can now send and receive attachments.

We allow the most common file types e.g. jpg .png and .pdf etc. And block harmful file types such as .exe.
You can send up to 10 attachments at a time.
Max attachment size 50 MB
